<item>
            <title>[LU-11632] OST pool tests in sanity, ost-pools, conf-sanity are failing</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11632</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Something has landed to master on November 6, 2018 that is causing tests that manipulate OST pools to fail. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here is what is failing:&lt;br/&gt;
ost-pools tests  1a, 1b, 1c, 1m, 1n, 2c, 2d, 2e, 3d, 4c, 5a, 5b, 6, 7a, 7c, 11, 12, 13, 15, 16, 17, 19, 20, 21, 22, 23a, 24, 25, 26 and 27 failing 100% of the time for review-dne-part-2 and review-dne-zfs-part-2&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;sanity (ost-pool tests) 200, 220, 406, 801c for review-dne-zfs-part-1&lt;br/&gt;
sanity tests 27D, 27G, 56wb, 200, 220, 406, 801c for review-dne-part-1&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;conf-sanity test 21c, 22, 23a, 23b, 24a, 24b, 25, 26, 27a, 27b, 28A, 28a, 29, 30a, 30b, 32a, 32d, 46a, 50f, 50g, 50h, 50i, 66 (timeout) for review-dne-part-3&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;conf-sanity tests 32a, 32d, 84, 108a (timeout) for review-zfs&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Passing: &lt;br/&gt;
review-ldiskfs (x86) .&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Some failing test sessions are at:&lt;br/&gt;
